text.tspan: FloodSense Gateway, Option A: Raspberry Pi & ItsyBitsy M4 + LoRa
- ItsyBitsy receives remote sensor data via LoRa;
- RPi receives data via serial connection to ItsyBitsy;
- RPi can store + serve data locally, analyze it, and/or relay to cloud;
- RPi can be used to reprogram remote nodes using standardized approach.
